## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| TOML serialization complexity for nested steps | Medium | Medium | Write comprehensive tests, use serde attributes |
| React Flow layout algorithm issues | Medium | Low | Use dagre or elkjs for auto-layout |
| Agent tool API design changes | Low | High | Keep tool schemas simple, version them |
| Step graph validation complexity | Medium | Medium | Start with simple cycle detection |

## Notes

- React Flow is already installed in the frontend (@xyflow/react)
- Hands page already has tab structure - add "Flow" tab alongside existing tabs
- Consider future Phase 2 when designing - visual editor will need the same API
- Step execution (Phase 3) will build on these data structures
